\b\fs32 1.About the Script System\b0\fs22\par
\b\fs28 1.a\par

\pard\widctlpar\li840\b0\fs22 There is a script system built into the program.It is fully  implemented by VB codes, and its grammar is similar to VB.I named it Tea Script.\par
\par
Scintilla is used in the script editor to provide the coloring function,so if SciLexer.dll is lost, you will not be able to write scripts in the level editor.However, if this happens, any script that already exists will still run without any problems.\par
\par
\f1 The script system enables you to manipulate nearly every object and variable in the game.You can make more advanced custom NPCs, blocks and even character states with this.\par
\par
In common case,you can run scripts you have written in the following 3 ways.\par
1.'Script' panel in events.\par
2.'Script' panel in liquids.\par
3.Directly run scripts in the built-in events of objects. Some special parameters are passed to the script.\par
